      "data": {
        "title": "Read the status strip first",
        "summary": "The toolbar is the authoritative summary surface. `Document` tells you what graph is open, `Save target` tells you where the next write is pointed, and `Access` tells you which installation context Twilite is using. If `Document` and `Save target` disagree, resolve that before writing.",
